Index: 1

[ValidTrueComment]:
The automated check verified that GNOME desktop environment is not installed on this XCP-ng Dom0 (RHEL 7-based) system. XCP-ng Dom0 is a headless hypervisor host that operates exclusively via command line and remote management interfaces (SSH, XenCenter, Xen Orchestra). Without a graphical user interface installed, this STIG requirement does not apply. The check confirmed that the gnome-desktop3 RPM package is not present on the system. Finding: Not Applicable.
        

