					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>To verify that null passwords cannot be used, run the following command: 

     # grep nullok /etc/pam.d/system-auth /etc/pam.d/password-auth

