If null passwords can be used, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>If an account is configured for password authentication but does not have an assigned password, it may be possible to log on to the account without authenticating.

