V-204486 - /dev/shm Mounted with Secure Options
============================================================

Command: mount | grep /dev/shm
Result: tmpfs on /dev/shm type tmpfs (rw,nosuid,nodev)

nodev: Present
nosuid: Present
noexec: MISSING

FAIL: /dev/shm is missing one or more required mount options.
Remediation: Add to /etc/fstab:
  tmpfs /dev/shm tmpfs defaults,nodev,nosuid,noexec 0 0
Then remount: mount -o remount /dev/shm
