					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Taking appropriate action in case of a filled audit storage volume will minimize the possibility of losing audit records.
One method of off-loading audit logs in Red Hat Enterprise Linux is with the use of the audisp-remote dameon.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
