					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the operating system generates audit records upon successful/unsuccessful attempts to use the "chmod", "fchmod", and "fchmodat" syscalls.

