					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The Red Hat Enterprise Linux operating system must audit all uses of the passwd command.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
