					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The Red Hat Enterprise Linux operating system must be configured so that all networked systems have SSH installed.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
