				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Responding to broadcast (ICMP) echoes facilitates network mapping and provides a vector for amplification attacks.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
