				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Restricting TFTP to a specific directory prevents remote users from copying, transferring, or overwriting system files.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
